{"name": "Wellfare - East Harlem Outpost", "alternate_name": "", "description": "* Located outside La Marqueta
* To register, a family must live in either Taft Houses or Johnson Houses (more developments to come soon).
* Families can register online at wellfare.org/signup, call (888) 574-9355 or visit a distribution to sign up in person
* Better Box program, a free monthly grocery subscription service for families living in eligible NYCHA public housing developments. Each Better Box has over $250 worth of better-for-you snacks, beverages, supplements and pantry goods. These boxes are shelf stable.
